#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:12 357f0fa593bf41d2a29d82b330465784
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 1.5 is a legacy release for lighter Chinese/English deployments and "
"existing 1.x workflows."
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.5 面向更轻量的中英部署与既有 1.x 工作流，属延续版本。"

