#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:17 1b1364898a4b4497884c2f217b33bf47
msgid ""
"We're thrilled to introduce a major upgrade that improves audio quality and "
"efficiency of VoxCPM, while maintaining the core capabilities of context-"
"aware speech generation and zero-shot voice cloning."
