#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:36 81c99e27eb1043808ed44d671ffa4e11
msgid ""
"For installation, loading, and the shared generation API, start with "
":doc:`../quickstart`."
msgstr "安装、加载与共用生成 API 请从 :doc:`../quickstart` 开始。"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:38 de226dbaa2424bdfa8b33c0d3e14659e
msgid ""
"Choose VoxCPM 1.5 when you want a lighter Chinese/English checkpoint than "
"VoxCPM 2 while keeping higher output quality than VoxCPM 1.0."
msgstr "若你需要比 VoxCPM 2 更轻的中英 checkpoint，同时又要比 VoxCPM 1.0 更高的输出质量，可选用 VoxCPM 1.5。"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:41 ca8a8646a8974a40bb0f6210ffaccd01
msgid "Model Updates"
msgstr "版本更新"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:44 5cf8cff36c614d018fcc87965e375d84
msgid "AudioVAE Sampling Rate: 16kHz -> 44.1kHz"
msgstr "AudioVAE Sampling Rate: 16kHz -> 44.1kHz"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:46 cdf93b9f1d1a47b99fffe01fc7cdf7c3
msgid "The AudioVAE now supports 44.1kHz sampling rate, which allows the model to:"
msgstr "AudioVAE 现已支持 44.1kHz 采样率，使模型能够："

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:48 a2bf2119fdcb4c84950e93745ac07e43
msgid "Better cloning fidelity with more preserved high-frequency detail"
msgstr "在保留更多高频细节的情况下提升克隆保真度"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:51 db59c2188c6541569e08489a84beec48
msgid ""
"This upgrade enables higher quality generation when using high-quality "
"reference audio, but does not guarantee that all generated audio will be "
"high-fidelity. The output quality depends on the **prompt speech** quality."
msgstr "在使用高质量参考音频时，这次升级有助于获得更高质量的生成结果，但并不保证所有生成音频都是高保真。输出质量取决于 **prompt 语音** 的质量。"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:54 f114e6a0b8ed417382a4ad46dc65cff1
msgid "Token Rate: 12.5Hz -> 6.25Hz"
msgstr "Token Rate: 12.5Hz -> 6.25Hz"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:56 020e223872124c76988c1da8e46360d7
msgid ""
"We reduced the token rate in LM from 12.5Hz to 6.25Hz (patch size increased "
"from 2 to 4) while maintaining similar performance on evaluation benchmarks."
" This change:"
msgstr "我们将 LM 中的 token 速率从 12.5Hz 降至 6.25Hz（patch 大小由 2 增至 4），同时在评测基准上保持相近表现。这一变化："

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:58 65d48e27f952419f8c8b6e198b522d0e
msgid "Reduces computational requirements for generating the same length of audio"
msgstr "降低生成相同时长音频的计算开销"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:59 9b3d8fca9fe24dd98119d53ece26c9fe
msgid "Provides a foundation for longer audio generation"
msgstr "为更长音频生成打下基础"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:62 08b31d4ab7e94a58bae13632368a54a5
msgid "Migration Guide"
msgstr "迁移指南"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:65 daa28e0c704d458da12476b1bed940ea
msgid "From VoxCPM-0.5B to VoxCPM1.5"
msgstr "从 VoxCPM-0.5B 到 VoxCPM 1.5"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:67 7b1847bb8e4346aabb9789a8ebac4282
msgid "**Update Model Path**: Point to VoxCPM1.5 checkpoint"
msgstr "**更新模型路径**：指向 VoxCPM1.5 checkpoint"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:68 6f67e865e45a4b0fba8aa7517d939914
msgid ""
"**Update Sample Rate**: Change ``sample_rate`` from ``16000`` to ``44100`` "
"in configs"
msgstr "**更新采样率**：在配置中将 ``sample_rate`` 从 ``16000`` 改为 ``44100``"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:69 72f6f103e6d6435886c2e67fb079c1d8
msgid ""
"**Update Audio Data**: The current fine-tuning pipeline automatically "
"resamples to 44.1kHz. If you preprocess offline, resample to 44.1kHz."
msgstr "**更新音频数据**：当前微调流水线会自动重采样到 44.1kHz。若你离线预处理，请重采样到 44.1kHz。"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:70 9e3397e01678421187784de0dfe6cfaf
msgid ""
"**Review Training Parameters**: Adjust batch size if needed due to higher "
"sampling rate"
msgstr "**检查训练参数**：因采样率提高，如有需要请调整 batch size"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:73 4f92c8101ea64184b803288d235ca68f
msgid "Backward Compatibility"
msgstr "向后兼容"

#: ../../models/voxcpm1.5.rst:75 e436867d97994202878b5d5b7aed14bd
msgid "VoxCPM-0.5B models and configurations remain fully supported"
msgstr "VoxCPM-0.5B 模型与配置仍完全受支持"

